First Gen May Build Gas-Fired, Hydro Power Plants, Bid for State Assets

-- B y   C e c i l i a   Y a p
-- 
2011-05-11T01:55:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-11/first-gen-may-build-gas-fired-hydro-power-plants-bid-for-state-assets.html
First Gen Corp. (FGEN)  may build a gas-fired
power plant beside its existing plants in Batangas province if
additional gas supplies from the Camago-Malampaya gas field in
Palawan is available, President Francis Giles Puno told
shareholders in a meeting in  Manila  today.  First Gen plans to build for power assets to be auctioned
by the government and is studying a plan to build hydropower
plants with combined capacity of 80 megawatts in the southern
Philippine island of Mindanao, Puno said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Cecilia Yap at 
 cyap19@bloomberg.net  